{"lastModified":1761578641026,"uri":"c::15366580866::vessel::ddd158f0-b13d-11ee-af5c-7d01dad09539","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Cairns, Queensland, Australia\n\nExplore the beauty of North Queensland in luxury and style aboard the Motor Yacht SEGARA. Built in 2013 by Shoreline Marine and extensively refitted in 2022, this 27m motor yacht boasts exceptional features and amenities that will make your journey a truly memorable one. Whether you're looking for an unforgettable holiday with your loved ones or a breathtaking venue for a\nspecial event, SEGARA has everything you need and more.\n\nSEGARA accommodates up to 8 guests overnight in 4 spacious guest suites, ensuring a comfortable and private experience for everyone on board. Additionally, the yacht can host up to 36 guests for special events or day charters, making it the perfect choice for corporate gatherings, weddings, or family celebrations. No matter the occasion, SEGARAS elegant and well-appointed living spaces will make you feel right at home.\n\nBased in far North Queensland, SEGARA offers a range of enchanting destinations for you to explore. Cruise through the stunning Whitsunday Islands, discover the wonders of Cairns or embark on an adventure to Port Douglas and beyond. With SEGARA you have the freedom to create your itinerary and experience the diverse beauty of North Queensland at your own\npace.\nStep onto SEGARA's large sundeck and soak up the sun while enjoying\nbreathtaking views of the surrounding landscapes. Lounge in style on the\ndeck's comfortable seating or dine alfresco with family and friends on the\nspacious aft deck. With SEGARA every moment spent on board is a moment of\npure bliss and relaxation.","blueprint":{"name":"SEGARA","images":["/media/media::image::c::15366580866::vessel::ddd158f0-b13d-11ee-af5c-7d01dad09539::assets::6088da80-b147-11ee-af5c-7d01dad09539.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::15366580866::vessel::ddd158f0-b13d-11ee-af5c-7d01dad0